<title>UK: BZW sets warrants on SAP.</title>
<headline>BZW sets warrants on SAP.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-08-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Deutschland branch of Barclays Plc said it has issued four million American-style call warrants, on SAP preference shares.</p>
<p>One preference share is controlled by 10 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    450 DEM		   ISSUE PRICE  8.14 DEM</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	03.AUG.98		 PAYDATE	20.AUG.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   FRANKFURT		 MIN EXER LOT 10</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  450 DEM</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
